channel.title: Isolate - INDIR3CT
channel.description:
So my tablet wasn't backed up and did an automatic IOS update that was corrupted.. couldn't restore it and had to reset it. Long story short because I didn't know it was updating It wasn't backed up.. and I lost a good amount of pictures, videos, oh and all my Auxy projects as well. And Im broke and don't pay for iCloud. Anyways I'm going through trying to salvage any shared Auxy files or older soundcloud private songs so I can at least get you something.
Heres a song I made a few months ago and never got around to posting... now its about all I got for you.. Sorry. Hope you like it.
https://soundcloud.com/indir3ct/isolate
